The paper proposes an extension of soft actor-critic for hierarchical deep Q-networks, which is a reinforcement learning technique. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses adversarial settings, which suggests that it could be related to game theory and multi-agent systems, leading to categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of mutual information metric, which is commonly used in computer vision and image processing, leading to categories such as cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
